  <title>Status Flagging Within Content</title>
  <body>
    <p status="new">This entire paragraph is status="new".</p>
    <p status="deleted">This entire paragraph is status="deleted".</p>
    <p status="changed">This entire paragraph is status="changed".</p>
    <p>Inline change marking [<ph status="deleted">this is deleted</ph><ph status="new">this is
        new</ph>] unchanged [<ph status="changed">changed</ph>].</p>
    <p rev="2.0">This paragraph is marked with rev="2.0".</p>
  </body>
